{"atom_id":"md_dmDM_ex_a175","atom_type":"FIGURE","file":"knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md","line_start":360,"line_end":388,"verbatim":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    Q[\"Which of the following five racial designations<br/>best describes you?<br/>(More than one choice is acceptable)<br/>RACE\"]\n    R1[\"☐ American Indian or Alaska Native\"]\n    R2[\"☐ Asian\"]\n    R3[\"☐ Black or African American\"]\n    R4[\"☐ Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander\"]\n    R5[\"☐ White\"]\n    R6[\"☐ Unknown\"]\n    R7[\"☐ Other\"]\n\n    Q --> R1\n    Q --> R2\n    Q --> R3\n    Q --> R4\n    Q --> R5\n    Q --> R6\n    Q --> R7\n\n    OTH[\"What was the other race?<br/>RACEOTH → SUPPDM.QVAL<br/>(QNAM = RACEOTH)\"]\n    UNK[\"If Unknown, please specify:<br/>RACEREAS → SUPPDM.QVAL<br/>(QNAM = RACEREAS)\"]\n\n    R7 -.->|\"If selected\"| OTH\n    R6 -.->|\"If selected\"| UNK\n\n    style Q fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px\n    style OTH fill:#eef5ff,stroke:#4a86c8\n    style UNK fill:#eef5ff,stroke:#4a86c8\n```","parent_section":"§DM.7 [Example 7]","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":"knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md L360-388 mermaid graph TD: Race designation CRF (5 racial designations + Unknown + Other) -> RACE; Other -> RACEOTH (SUPPDM.QVAL QNAM=RACEOTH); Unknown -> RACEREAS (SUPPDM.QVAL QNAM=RACEREAS)","cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt_version":"P0_writer_md_v1.9.1","ts":"2026-05-06T10:14:00Z"}}
